Content-Type: application/json

{
  "code": "GER-001",
  "name": "Gerencia de Operaciones"
}

### Create gerencia — duplicate code (expect 409)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/organization/gerencias
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "code": "GER-001",
  "name": "Duplicada"
}

